Lassi-Items.name: Sweet Lassi
Lassi-Items.Description: lassi, a creamy, frothy yogurt-based drink, blended with water and various fruits or seasonings (such as salt or sugar)

Lassi-Items.name: Fruit Lassi
Lassi-Items.Description: Fruit lassi is a traditional Indian drink made with yogurt (dahi) and mango, also used in Ayurvedic medicine to purify the body and the spirit, and that is also great for taming the heat of spicy dishes

Lassi-Items.name: Mango Lassi
Lassi-Items.Description: Mango lassi is a traditional Indian drink made with yogurt (dahi) and mango, also used in Ayurvedic medicine to purify the body and the spirit, and that is also great for taming the heat of spicy dishes

Lassi-Items.name: Dry Fruit Lassi
Lassi-Items.Description: Lassi is a proper traditional yoghurt based drink. It is a blend of yoghurt, water, spices, dry fruits and sometimes tropical fruits

Lassi-Items.name: Chocolate Lassi
Lassi-Items.Description: Chocolate Lassi is a flavoured refreshing drink made by blending curd with chocolate shavings, coco powder & sugar. Chocolate Lassi beats the summer heat and could be made in minutes. Chocolate Lassi is filling, delicious and the family will come for more

Lassi-Items.name: Strawberry Lassi
Lassi-Items.Description: Strawberry lassi is a creamy, fruity, rose scented lassi made with yogurt, strawberries, cream and rose water

Lassi-Items.name: Blueberry Lassi
Lassi-Items.Description: nchanting Banana Blueberry Lassi is a yogurt based smoothie, which is considered to be a healthy & nutritious drink.

Lassi-Items.name: Mango Lassi with Peri Peri Fries
Lassi-Items.Description: It's made from ground coriander, salt, garlic powder, onion powder, dried oregano, dried parsley, paprika, ground nutmeg, ground ginger, ground cardamom, smoked paprika, and cayenne pepper

Lassi-Items.name: Sweet Lassi with Cheese Corn Nuggets
Lassi-Items.Description: It has a cheey and cremy texture with delicious sweet corns in it that is further finely coated in crispy golden bread crumbs.

Lassi-Items.name: Kiwi Lassi with Chilli Garlic Pops
Lassi-Items.Description: Blend kiwi pieces, thick yoghurt, honey and vanilla extract with enough water to make a smooth drink.

Lassi-Items.name: Oreo Shake
Lassi-Items.Description: Made with Oreo cookies, milk, vanilla ice cream, sugar, and chocolate sauce, this thick oreo shake recipe will take over your taste buds

Lassi-Items.name: Oreo Chips Shake
Lassi-Items.Description: Chocolate milk is made with milk and chocolate syrup (usually made with cocoa powder, sugar, and a bit of water) and a chocolate milkshake is made with milk, chocolate syrup, and ice cream, so it's much richer, thicker, and frostier.

Lassi-Items.name: Nutella Oreo Shake
Lassi-Items.Description: Nutella Milkshake is a delicious recipe made using just 3 simple ingredients â€“ chilled milk, vanilla ice cream, and Nutella. It gets its rich and creamy texture from vanilla ice cream and the chocolaty, nutty flavor from Nutella.

Lassi-Items.name: Oreo Coffee
Lassi-Items.Description: The addition of Oreos gives the classic cold coffee a nice chocolaty and creamy texture and makes it even more delicious.

Lassi-Items.name: Nutella Coffee
Lassi-Items.Description: Nutella Coffee is a delicious beverage where your regular frothy coffee is mixed with Nutella

Lassi-Items.name: KitKat Coffee
Lassi-Items.Description: Nestle Kit Kat Chocolate Coffee Break is the moderately sweet chocolate which is the perfect aftertaste for Gold Blend, which is mild and low in acidity

Lassi-Items.name: Strawberry Banana Smoothie with Ice Cream
Lassi-Items.Description: A strawberry-Banana smoothie is a great source of protein, fibre, vitamins and minerals, and it helps with hydration.

Lassi-Items.name: Mango Banana Smoothie with Ice Cream
Lassi-Items.Description: Combine mangos, banana, vanilla yogurt, and milk in a blender; blend until smooth.

Lassi-Items.name: Blueberry Smoothie with Ice Cream
Lassi-Items.Description: Packed with antioxidants, they pack a lot of nutrients into a small, low-calorie package. You get a generous dose of fiber, Vitamin C, Vitamin K, and manganese in every one cup serving of blueberries.
